            <p class="text-white/80">Experience without evidence. Intuition without insight. Recommendations that sound good but lack measurable foundations.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-red-400 pl-6">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-white mb-2">Junior Delivery</h4>
            <p class="text-white/80">Hand-offs to inexperienced teams. Cookie-cutter solutions. No continuity between strategy and implementation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: The Solution -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">The Lighthouse Difference</h3>
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-3xl p-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-[#00D4AA] rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
